<h2 id="coding-the-subordinate-collection">Coding the Subordinate Collection <a class="headerlink" href="subordinate-resource-endpoint#coding-the-subordinate-collection" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Test, check! Let's hook this up. Open <code>ProgrammerController</code>. At first, it's pretty
easy. Exchange the <code>nickname</code> for a <code>Programmer</code> object. I'll use a magic param
converter for this: just type-hint the argument with <code>Programmer</code>, and it will
magically make the query for us:</p>
